summary: Iconic A-Frame type home, with a great view of whiterun.
descriptionHtml:
[center][size=2][img=center]https://snag.gy/Xvb5Cd.jpg[/img][/size]

[u][size=6]WHITERUN VIEW[/size]

[/u][size=4]Live in the iconic A-Frame style house, a small cabin perfect for the adventurer located near Riverwood.
Includes one of the best views for a forge, and there is a guard outside.
[/size]
[u][size=5]Includes organized named containers[/size][/u]
[size=4]For; Ingots, pelts, armor, arrows, bows, potions, soul gems, books and junk.[/size]

[size=5]Installation[/size]
[size=3]Manually: Just extract the .esp and drop it into your data folder then load it.

[/size]Any bugs you find please post them in the bug section, if the ore vein and planters don't work just make sure to wait in-game 2 days so they can activate.

[color=#ffff00]If your updating this mod you [u]HAVE[/u] to empty out all the chests associated with my mod since they are [i]unique[/i] containers.[/color]
